sub_title: 2.9 billion people are still not online. A problem worth solving
summary:
Founder of wasoe.com, we build, host and support the future of everything digital. Now exploring the possibilities of web3.

Based in the Netherlands, but is investing and operating in Bansko, Bulgaria through banskolab.com where we teach kids how to code & how to start companies, our youngest entrepreneur is 9 years old. 

I believe that digital Inclusion is a problem worth solving, the question is how? 

I am interested in reg tech, blockchain, web3, circular economy and everything that makes the world a better place.
